#

Tuna Salad Toast

10 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishWheat

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Lunch

Tags:

Quick MealLunchHealthy

Description

A quick and satisfying meal featuring creamy tuna salad on crispy toast, perfect for any time of the day.

Ingredients

  • canned tuna: 1 can (5 oz)
  • mayonnaise: 2 tablespoons
  • celery, diced: 1/4 cup
  • red onion, diced: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 1 tablespoon
  • whole grain bread: 2 slices
  • salt: to taste
  • black pepper: to taste
  • dill, chopped (optional): 1 tablespoon
